<p>Free tools are not a marketing gimmick. They are a structural advantage in organic search.</p>
<p>Stratabeat analyzed 300 B2B SaaS websites and 15,000 data points in their <a href="https://stratabeat.com/b2b-saas-seo-performance-report-released/">2025 B2B SaaS SEO Performance Report</a>. The study compared websites that offered free online tools against those that did not. The results were not close.</p>
